*Stingtra climbs onto a big hill and stands on the top of it*

Stingtra: I've wished I've had a better chance....I just hope I have a
chance of getting in.....

*Stingtra says to the sky thinking she's talking to the Matrix. Stingtra
steps closer*

Stingtra: Sorry Megatron, but I just can't stand life anymore...Sorry
DarkMouse, You were okay and didn't want to hurt me to just tell me that no
one liked me....Sorry KitKat, I was going to fix your limb but it appears
that you found better bots to do that....Sorry Quickstrike, I loved you,
but, killing myself is probably doing you a favor, so this is my present to
you......

*Stingtra jumps off the hill and crashes into many rocks and most banging
her in the head. 40 more rocks hit her hard in the head and she finally
rolls to end and rolls on ground and stops in the middle of both Predacon
Bases. Mech Tears run out of Stingtra's optics as she lays there but just in
stasis lock, for the hill was not big enough*
